- Žao mi je, gospodine.

764
01:40:37,542 --> 01:40:40,375
To važi i za ovu lepu mladu damu.

765
01:40:41,250 --> 01:40:43,833
Ne bi trebalo da skrnavite
nacionalna blaga!

766
01:40:46,000 --> 01:40:47,375
